items.text: Essentials first. Autopay must be verified. Discretionary blocked if obligations not covered. Always keep capital buffer above minimum.
Target properties must have positive cashflow. Minimum cap rate 8%. Location critical for tenant quality. Avoid high-vacancy areas. Focus on workforce housing or student housing.
